Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: fnctl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, adduser
Description: Self-hosted function runtime and CLI (Lambda-like)
 A tiny, dependency-free server and CLI to run self-hosted
 functions that can be invoked via HTTP. Includes create/destroy/list,
 optional per-function logging, and an extendable runtime model.
